description.en: Deno is a runtime for JavaScript and TypeScript that is based on the V8 JavaScript engine and the Rust programming language. It was created by Ryan Dahl, original creator of Node.js, and is focused on productivity.
description.ga_IE: Is Runtime é Deno le haghaidh JavaScript agus Ceolchríochnaithe atá bunaithe ar an Inneall JavaScript V8 agus ar an teanga chláraithe meirge.Chruthaigh Ryan Dahl é, cruthaitheoir bunaidh node.js, agus tá sé dírithe ar tháirgiúlacht.
